Sep 20, 2019
Experimental strategy to improve accuracy of SuperTrend Cloud. I am attempting to use STD deviation to manipulate the multiplier of the SuperTrend cloud. Greater STD Deviation = Oscillation in price action which can be applied to multiplier of SuperTrend to filter out bad trades and improve accuracy.
Sep 21, 2019
Release Notes
Many times we make mistakes trading because we become impatient and want to be in a trade due to emotions. This mentality makes it easy to loose money.

Ideally we should only long above the cloud however, I have added longs on oversold RSI conditions + Below SuperTrend Cloud which has done a great job increasing profits and allowing us to maintain accuracy and increase profit potentials.
