Oct 6, 2019
Release Notes
-Cleaned up code
-Added inputs for both SuperTrend clouds to make it more adjustable.
-Added SL line (center of cloud).
-Added option to only exit after fully crossing cloud.

A good starting point is 5m charts use 10,6,6,10 (Multiplier 1, Period 1, Multiplier 2, Period 2) or 4h Chart 3,10,6,10 (Multiplier 1, Period 1, Multiplier 2, Period 2)

BTC performs well on 4h chart with 2.4,4,4.8,4 (Multiplier 1, Period 1, Multiplier 2, Period 2)
Oct 8, 2019
Release Notes
-Fixed duplicate trade issue
